    "body": "Got it thanks  ! there are two formulas  : \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3207061/52335672-a43d5300-2a0b-11e9-8698-10c0c5389f69.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3207061/52335674-a9020700-2a0b-11e9-9aee-f0727ecb04b0.png)\r\n\r\nPandas applies the second formula and instead of S2 = moving average of Y1 & Y2  it starts from S1 = Y1  . \r\n\r\nSo instead of :\r\n`df.iloc[:2] = seed_ewm`\r\nIt should be : \r\n`df.iloc[:1] = seed_ewm`\r\n\r\nand the result is :\r\n\r\n   \r\n0         NaN\r\n1   16.833333\r\n2  272.277778\r\n3   91.425926\r\n4   31.141975\r\n5   11.047325\r\n\r\nThank you !"
